    <span style="font-size: 35px;"> Asir City Location:</span><br>
    The Asir area, named after the Asir tribe, is one of the Saudi cities through which the Sarawat Mountains pass in the southwest of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. <br><br>
    
    <span style="font-size: 35px;"> Climate in Asir:</span><br>
    Asir is one of the coldest areas in Saudi Arabia during wintertime, with an average temperature of about 29 degrees Celsius, and its weather has encouraged the tourism boom in Asir compared to other cities.
    <br>
    <br>
    <span style="font-size: 35px;"> Distribution of Tourism places:</span><br>

